
Introduction
------------

This is simple pcap based program to sniff Maniac Challenge 2013 related packets in a network to monitor the operations. It does the following.

- Dumps the information of the different Maniac Challenge packets (ADVERT, BID, BIDWIN & DATA)
- Computes & dumps the balances of each IP address


Compilation
----------- 

make linux


Running
-------

./maniac-sniffer-linux eth1

where eth1 is the network interface connected to the OLSR network
